{
  "stem": "95.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And again, I've got a piece of bread and margarine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We worked hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had really a maniac SS guard there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, it's the same guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He would shoot at random.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He would-- He would scream and hit us constantly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He did something that we will-- we will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "One day at the camp-- at the factory, there was a man who took a useless piece of wire on the ground.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know what he wanted to do with it-- I assume he wanted to make a belt, because his pants were falling, no belt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he hits him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he hits the two guys next-- next to him, who did nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were there next to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He hits them violently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And one of the-- the kapos who was taking care of these three guys was a remarkable man from Belgium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he went to this-- we called him Tom Mix.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we all called him Tom Mix, because he thought he was an American cowboy movie stars of the '30s.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was riding a bicycle like a cowboy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was holding his-- his guns like a cowboy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was walking like a-- like John Wayne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went to this Tom Mix, said, why are you doing this?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why are you hitting them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a useless piece of wire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he hits him too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I saw a lot of hangings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these four people a few days later were hanged, just because this one individual stole a useless piece of wire that was-- he was caught by Tom Mix.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just-- the first hanging I saw-- and I'm a kid who was absolutely scared of everything when I was a child.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
